![Charging Profile charts showing Voltage, Current, Power, SoC and CC→CV transition](/Users/overwatch/.gemini/antigravity/brain/1ba26a82-272e-4b4c-9008-05ffacde93d1/charging_profile_charts_1773131231979.png)
