### 2. Configurable Parameters

| Parameter | Range | Default |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| Battery Capacity | 20–100 kWh | 60 kWh |
| Nominal Voltage | 200–800 V | 400 V |
| Initial SoC | 5–90% | 20% |
| Target SoC | 50–100% | 100% |
| Charging Level | L1 (1.4kW) to DC Ultra-Fast (350kW) | L2 (7.2kW) |
| Converter Topology | LLC / LCL / Vienna / Full-Bridge | LLC |
| CC→CV Transition | 60–90% SoC | 80% |
| Charger Efficiency | 85–99% | 96% |

### 3. Harmonic Analysis

The simulator computes **real-time harmonic injection** based on the selected converter topology:

| Topology | THD (CC) | THD (CV) | Efficiency |
|----------|----------|----------|------------|
| **LLC Resonant** | 4.2% | 2.1% | 98% |
| **LCL Resonant** | 5.1% | 2.8% | 96.7% |
| **Vienna Rectifier** | 3.8% | 1.9% | 97% |
| **Full-Bridge** | 7.2% | 4.0% | 95% |

Features:
- **Grid current waveform** showing distorted sinusoid at PCC
- **Harmonic spectrum** (3rd through 19th) with IEEE 519 limit line
- **THD vs SoC** plot showing how harmonics change during charging
- **IEEE 519-2022 compliance check** with pass/fail status

### 4. Multi-EV Grid Impact

![Multi-EV aggregate load simulation with peak demand of 71.9 kW](/Users/overwatch/.gemini/antigravity/brain/1ba26a82-272e-4b4c-9008-05ffacde93d1/grid_impact_results_1773131262370.png)

Simulates **1–20 EVs** charging simultaneously with:
- Random battery sizes, charging levels, and initial SoC values
- **Aggregate load profile** over 4 hours
- **Transformer loading %** with overload detection
- **Load distribution** (stacked area: CC / CV / Done)
- **Fleet status table** showing each EV's parameters

