This simulator directly addresses the **"What You Plan to Do Next"** items from your meeting prep notes:

- [x] **Model the CC-CV charging profile** mathematically — ✅ Power draw as function of time/SoC
- [x] **Simulate the harmonic injection** during CC vs CV modes — ✅ Per-topology harmonic spectra
- [x] **Analyze the aggregate effect** of multiple EVs — ✅ Multi-EV simulation with transformer loading
- [x] **Compare converter topology impacts on THD** — ✅ LLC vs LCL vs Vienna vs Full-Bridge
- [x] **IEEE 519 compliance check** — ✅ Real-time pass/fail assessment

> [!TIP]
> Try switching between **LLC** and **Full-Bridge** topologies to see how the harmonic profile changes. The Full-Bridge has THD of 7.2% during CC mode, which **violates IEEE 519**!
